propClasses: Override or extend the styles applied to the component.
propColor: The color of the component. It supports those theme colors that make sense for this component.
propDisableAnimation: If `true`, the transition animation is disabled.
propError: If `true`, the label is displayed in an error state.
propFocused: If `true`, the input of this label is focused.
propMargin:
If `dense`, will adjust vertical spacing. This is normally obtained via context from
FormControl.
propRequired: if `true`, the label will indicate that the input is required.
stylesRoot: Styles applied to the root element.
stylesFocused: Pseudo-class applied to the root element if `focused={true}`.
stylesDisabled: Pseudo-class applied to the root element if `disabled={true}`.
stylesError: Pseudo-class applied to the root element if `error={true}`.
stylesRequired: Pseudo-class applied to the root element if `required={true}`.
stylesAsterisk: Pseudo-class applied to the asterisk element.
stylesFormControl: Styles applied to the root element if the component is a descendant of `FormControl`.
stylesMarginDense: Styles applied to the root element if `margin="dense"`.
stylesShrink: Styles applied to the `input` element if `shrink={true}`.
stylesAnimated: Styles applied to the `input` element unless `disableAnimation={true}`.
stylesFilled: Styles applied to the root element if `variant="filled"`.
stylesOutlined: Styles applied to the root element if `variant="outlined"`.
